source.name: Number of Well Bores Started (Spud) During the Fiscal Year on Federal Lands
source.description: This table contains the total number of well bores started (spudded), by state, during each fiscal year. "Spudding in," or to "spud" a well bore, means to begin drilling operations, so a spudded well bore is one where drilling operations have begun.
